So here you can now choose your state from drop-down menu.
If there is no your state, you can write it manualy.
If you write your state manualy, you need to write Tax Rate % by yourself.
Now there is no automatic discount calc., you need to write ur discount % manualy.
It make my calc useful for a wide variety of situations.
All info (even if auto) will be written over total value.
